Caumnda introduced DelegateExecutionFake object for testing purpose. Use it instead of mocking, and the test would be much simpler and more valuable. Use also AssertJ lib, is cleaner. 

    public void execute_shouldSetValidUuidAsPnfUuid() {
        // given
        GeneratePnfUuidDelegate delegate = new GeneratePnfUuidDelegate();
        DelegateExecutionFake execution = new DelegateExecutionFake();
        // when
        delegate.execute(execution);
        //then
        assertThat((String)execution.getVariable(PNF_UUID)).matches(PnfCheckInputs.UUID_REGEX);
    }
